
  Kommo-o    Dragon Type Pokémon

  When it spots enemies, it threatens 
  them by jingling the scales on 
  its tail.  Weak opponents will 
  crack and flee in panic. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Jangmo-o ► Hakamo-o ► Kommo-o

